                  <FONT COLOR='#FFFFFF' SIZE='10' KERNING='0' LETTERSPACING='0' FACE='Verdana'>FLABER basically works with the principle illustrated in the diagram besides. It involves a Flash administrative backend system to build some data in XML format or database format through the PHP Server. And then the Flash frontend will pull the data out to generate a Flash format website. Or a PHP frontend will pull the data out to generate a HTML format website.</FONT>
